Feature: Hotel Booking In Adactin Application 

Scenario: User Login In Adactin Application 

	Given user Launch The Web Application 
	When user Enter The Username In Username Field 
	And user Enter The Password In Password Field 
	Then user Click The Login Button And Navigates To Search Hotel Page 
	
Scenario: New User Registration Form 

	When user Enter The Username In UserName Field 
	And user Enter The Password In Password Field 
	And user Enter The Confirm Password In Confirm Password Field 
	And user Enter The Fullname In Fullname Field 
	And user Enter The Email Address In Email Address Field 
	And user Enter The Captcha Text In Captcha Text Field What Is There In Captcha Image Field 
	Then user Click The Terms/Conditions And Register The Form 
	 